331
00:49:10,458 --> 00:49:13,578
You're the one who's changed.

332
00:49:18,833 --> 00:49:23,423
Ever since you've been
with movie people.

333
00:49:23,583 --> 00:49:26,623
You used to write crime novels.

334
00:49:26,791 --> 00:49:32,251
We didn't have much money,
but everything was fine.

335
00:49:39,833 --> 00:49:46,003
