345
00:50:36,875 --> 00:50:40,915
When Prokosch calls,
tell him l won't talk to him.

346
00:50:41,916 --> 00:50:45,076
Paul, come here.

347
00:50:48,458 --> 00:50:51,618
Why won't you do the script now?

348
00:50:54,458 --> 00:50:57,578
I'd have done it out of love for you.

349
00:50:59,958 --> 00:51:03,618
