364
00:52:15,625 --> 00:52:20,865
- First tell me if it's true.
- No, you tell me first.

365
00:52:22,208 --> 00:52:25,538
What makes me think
you've stopped loving me?

366
00:52:25,708 --> 00:52:28,708
